plugin.description:
Integrates News Manager with the SA GS Admin Toolbar. Adds top level links (tabs) to:
- News Manager main admin page - Create new post - Edit post (if viewing a post in the frontend)
Requires: - SA GS Admin Toolbar &lt;http://get-simple.info/extend/plugin/sa-gs-admin-toolbar/483&gt; - News Manager &lt;http://get-simple.info/extend/plugin/news-manager-updated/541/&gt;

This plugin displays a map of Google Maps on your GetSimple website.

&lt;b&gt;Features:&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple maps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple markers on each map.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Icons / Markers customizable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Different types of map.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Selection of controls of the map.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

Included languages: English, German, Spanish

&lt;b&gt;Latest version: 2.0 (1/apr/2012)&lt;/b&gt;
 
(Tested in version GS 3.0 and 3.1. Does not work with earlier versions.)

More info in support forum.

