Add a guestbook to your site easily.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Description and Features:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
------------------------------------------
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;This plugin adds a &#039;Guestbook&#039; to any GetSimple page which records and displays visitors&#039; comments. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Visitors can reply to comments making threaded conversations. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comments are arranged into numbered pages. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comments are displayed in chronological or reverse chronological order.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comments are saved with separate backups.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Email notifications of new comments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unwanted comments can be deleted through the GetSimple Admin Pages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BBCode is supported for comment writing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Emoticons are supported in comments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Emoticons can be added to and deleted from the library or completely turned off.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guestbook appearance can be styled with standard CSS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CAPTCHA is included to eliminate spam.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It is possible limit the number of characters by post&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Versions:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
-----------------------&lt;br /&gt;
