Lightbox is a plug-in for displaying full-size images from thumbnails and for creating simple image galleries.

Lightbox requires a link to a jQuery library in your page template.

-  To use the plugin simply insert a GetSimple thumbnail image into your page content using the button of the CKEditor;
- The plugin is customisable with 35 further settings available in the GetSimple Admin;
- The Setup page contains all the necessary instructions for usage;
- Language files are supported with English and Russian already included.

The plugin front end can be seen on the Demo Page **[Test website](http://fortest.infobizar.ru/uslugi/)**!

