&quot;eShop for RA&quot; is not separate theme. This is the add-on to the theme &quot;Red Agency&quot;, which expands the possibilities of this theme.&lt;br&gt;
Add-on &quot;eShop for RA&quot;, by using appropriate plugins, will allow you to create fully-fledged e-commerce sites (catalogs, shopping basket and so on). Similar to those that used by specialized e-commerce CMS (as PrestaShop, Magento, ZenCart and others).&lt;br&gt;
